text: Welcome to the charming Glenhaven community, nestled along peaceful Cain Lake. This 1372 sqft property offers 2 spacious bedrooms plus an additional den/office. The newly renovated kitchen features quartz countertops and fresh appliances. Many recent upgrades, including a new furnace, water heater and roof. The perfect multifamily investment in growing and appreciating Blaine WA. Walking distance to Canadian border. Incredible income potential in 1 bed and 2 bed single level units with decks. Large 11, 000 sf lot allows for so much flexibility for the future. 1, 400+ sf heated shop split into 4 separate rentable areas would make great storage for renters, additional income, and/or owner use. This property has space to roam! At over 4, 300 square feet and close to a comfort station, this large corner lot is spacious and private feeling. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Welcome to your cozy haven in one of Bellingham's premier all ages mobile home parks! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a viewing today!

Discover a prime 3.2-acre piece of vacant land on Semiahmoo Drive. Welcome to this charming newly refreshed 1910 home! This is a 2+ bedroom home loaded with windows and light. Large kitchen with lots of cabinets for storage. Spacious bathroom has large tiled shower. Don't miss seeing this home today.

HOT PRICED 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Craftsman charmer in the popular Bay Crest neighborhood featuring downstairs open concept kitchen/ dining & two living room layout with gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, ceiling fans and laundry room.Upstairs features 2 spacious bedrooms that share a full bathroom & a roomy primary with walk-in closet, really nice en suite with dual sink vanity, separate shower & jetted tub! Amazing condo in the heart of Bellingham, located close to amenities, entertainment, local farmers market, & I-5. This 5th story condo w/elevator access features new floors, light fixtures & paint. neighborhoods: City Center Bellingham, Downtown District Bellingham
